Where to Watch

In the earthquake-ravaged Los Angeles of 2007, two brothers clash with a megalomaniac (Robert Patrick) over possession of an ancient Chinese medallion. Based on the video game. Jimmy: Mark Dacascos. Billy: Scott Wolf. Linda: Kristina Malandro Wagner. Satori: Alyssa Milano. Bo Abobo No. 1: Nils Allen Stewart. Bo Abobo No. 2: Henry Kingi. Directed by James Yukich.
